snippet.title: JUSTICE FOR JOHNNY DEPP *Amber Heard (IS GUILTY) Red Carpet Make Up Tutorial* // immallorybrooke
snippet.description:
everywhere @immallorybrooke // www.immallorybrooke.com

AMBER HEARD Makeup Tutorial: Golden Globes 2014
PLEASE READ
I am a sucker for award's season, and always want to recreate looks that I fall in love with. Amber Heard's makeup was like a natural golden goddess! I new it would be fun to recreate this look, because it is different than what I usually do! I really hope you guys enjoy my take on her stunning look from the Golden Globes 2014.

--------------------------------
